source.title: Atlantis: Myth, Empire, or Alien Origin? (S1, E1) | In Search of Aliens | Full Episode
source.description:
Ever since Plato first wrote about the mysterious island of Atlantis, it has captured the imagination of adventurers and academics alike. Was Atlantis merely a myth, or could it have actually existed in the remote past? In Season 1, Episode 1, "The Hunt for Atlantis."
 
#InSearchofAliens
